      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bahr teem Praweescheem.\nManna Sirds tohp manna\nWiddû lausita / wiſſi manni\nKauli drebb/ es efmu ka weens\npeedſehris Wihrs/ un ka weens/\nfo tas Wihrs pahrwarre / ta\nKUNGA Preekscha/ un preeksch\nteem Wahrdeem winna Sweh-\ntivas."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ta Semme irr pilna\nPaulibaß-Pahrkahpaju / jo ta\nSemme behdajahs to Lahstu\ndeht/ tahs Tuksnefes Gannibas\niskalst/ tadeht ka winno Bah-\nschana tauna irraid/ un winno\nWaldischana ne irr pareist."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tik labbi tas Praweets\nka Preesteris irr apblehnoju-\nschees / patt manna Namma\natrohmu es winno Blehdibu /\nfakka tas KUNGS:"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz buhs winnu Zeffsch\nka fliddenas Weetas Tumsiba /\npee ka tee peedausifees un krit-\ntihs. Jo es weddifchu pahr teem\nLaununu winnu Beeineklecha-\nnas Gadda/ fakka tas KUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gann es pee teem Pra-\ntweescheem eekſch Samarijas re-\ndfeju aplamas Leetas/ jo tee flud-\ndinaja zaur Baalu/ un peewihle\nmannus Israeta Laudis."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet pee teem Prawee-\nscheem eekſch Jerusalemes redsn\ne Negantibu/ tee pahrkahpj to\nLautibu/ un tinnahs ar Wiltri-\nbu/ un stiprina to Launadarri-"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz fakka tas KUNGS\nZebaot no fscheim Praweescheen\nta: Rauqi/ es ebdinaschu tohe\nar Wehrmelehjn/un dsirdinaschu\ntohs ar Schulta Uhdeni/ jo ne\nteem Jerusalemes Praweescheen\nirr ta Blehdiba isgahjuti wiſſa\nSemmê."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta fakka tas KUNGS\nZebaot: Ne klaufajt to Prawee-\nschu Wahrdeem/ kas jums flud-\ndina/ tee darra juhs neleeſchus/\ntee runna fawas Sirds Parah-\nditchanu / ne no ta KUNGS\nMuttes."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee fakka allaschix uhe-\nteem/ kas manni faimo : Tas\nKUNGS irr to runnajs / fa-\njums Meers buhs/ un uhe wis-\nfeem / kas pehz fawa Sirde-\nPrahta staiga / fakka tee: Pab-\njums ne nahks Launums."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo kas irr eekſch ta KUN-\nGA Padohma stahwejs? uu-\nwinnu Wahrdiu redsejs jeb dsir-\ndejs? Kas irr winna Wahrdi-\nwehra jehmis un klaufsjs?"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rauqi / ta KUNGS\nWehtra zelſees ar Bahrsibu/ i-\nweena pastahwiga Wehtra / ta-\nkrittibs us to Besdeewigo Gal-\nwu."
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta KUNGA Bahrsibu\nne greesifees atpakkat / teekam-\nta irr darrijsi/ un tamehr ta ir-\neezeł"
    }
  ],
